Product name: Fleece Dog Pajamas, Dog PJs, Dog Jammies, Dog Clothes, Pet Clothes, Pet Pajamas, Support Animal Rescue, Custom Dog Clothes, Dog Onesie
Description:
Soft and cuddly fleece pajamas for your pup! Keep them warm and extra cute with their own cozy dog clothes. These PJs are sewn by me and made with love. I buy my fabric in small batches, so these jammies are super unique and one-of-a-kind!
Three different neck options to choose from! Standard collar, snood (which is like a dog turtleneck), or hood (like a hooded sweatshirt). 
These sizes are pretty forgiving, as the fabric is stretchy, and also, dogs don't generally care whether their clothes fit perfectly, but please do your best to wrangle your pup and get some measurements (pro tip: bring cookies).

* LENGTH - from base of neck to tail (dog must be standing)
* WIDTH - of chest, all the way around, right behind armpits
* NECK - circumference, right below where the collar would sit
* LEGS - is your dog tall, short, or average?

***IMPORTANT: If I do not have your dog's measurements by FIVE business days before your order is scheduled to ship, you will receive a generic size instead of a custom pair. These may not fit as well as a pair that are made to your dog's specific measurements, but if you would like a pair that is custom made, you MUST provide your dog's measurements. 
***A portion of each purchase will be donated to either Brew City Bully Club, our local pitbull advocacy and rehab/rescue organization, OR Canine Cupids, a rescue organization whose mission is to protect and improve the lives of Milwaukee's homeless, neglected, and exceptional needs dogs and to place them in permanent, loving homes.***
